Package: nexus-mp-docker
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusMP - Docker IMAP4rev1 Mail Server
 A high-performance IMAP4rev1 mail server for Docker containers.
 Supports IDLE, compression, STARTTLS, and advanced mail management.

Package: nexus-mta-docker
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusMTA - Docker Mail Transfer Agent
 A lightweight Mail Transfer Agent for Docker containers.
 Handles SMTP queue processing and mail routing.

Package: nexus-smtp-docker
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusSMTP - Docker SMTP Server
 A robust SMTP server for Docker containers.
 Handles incoming mail submission and routing.

Package: nexus-rmc-docker
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: NexusRMC - Docker Remote Mail Client
 A command-line remote mail client with DKIM/DMARC/SPF support.
 Manages remote mail operations and security checks.
